ce uncertainties on MINERvA's absolute cross\nsection measurements, and demonstrates a technique that can be used in future\nneutrino beams such as LBNF.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 31 May 2019 22:43:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 26 Mar 2021 17:08:02 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 21 Oct 2021 18:25:14 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 24 Feb 2022 22:33:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-28"}
