st RDMM and LDDMM estimations. Our code\nwill be open-sourced. Code is available at\nhttps://github.com/uncbiag/registration.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 1 Jun 2019 03:14:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 9 Nov 2019 03:19:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-12"}
