peal to\nestimated sequence and prove the complexity bound of\n$\\widetilde{O}(n^{7/3}\\varepsilon^{-4/3})$. As such, we see that accelerated\nvariant of Sinkhorn outperforms Sinkhorn and Greenkhorn in terms of\n$1/\\varepsilon$ and APDAGD and accelerated alternating minimization\n(AAM)~\\citep{Guminov-2021-Combination} in terms of $n$. Finally, we conduct the\nexperiments on synthetic and real data and the numerical results show the\nefficiency of Greenkhorn, APDAMD and accelerated Sinkhorn in practice.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 1 Jun 2019 05:33:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 9 Jun 2019 07:16:49 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 22 Jun 2019 04:21:58 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sun, 4 Aug 2019 18:15:07 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Thu, 17 Oct 2019 23:25:15 GMT"},{"version":"v6","created":"Tue, 24 Mar 2020 02:50:47 GMT"},{"version":"v7","created":"Sun, 1 Aug 2021 05:06:20 GMT"},{"version":"v8","created":"Wed, 23 Mar 2022 04:19:53 GMT"},{"version":"v9","created":"Tue, 17 May 2022 18:35:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-19"}
